 These rules define local execution within an actor.
 
\noun on
ExprHole 
\noun default
allows execution to propagate to the context, and also determines the order
 of evaluation for complex expressions.
 
\noun on
Fld,
\noun default
 
\noun on
DeclLocal
\noun default
, and
\noun on
